&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;When restart in restartClient the client instance is null and (line 284)&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;if (client.isHandshook()) {&lt;br/&gt;
&#160;&#160;&#160; LOG.info(&quot;Successfully restarted!&quot;);&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;raise NPE.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;probably the patch:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;if (client != null &amp;amp;&amp;amp; client.isHandshook()) { ....&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;fix this.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;When error occur Salesforce subscription never restart. We must restart services.&lt;/p&gt;

